-- BMW, Honda, Ford, VW Among Finalists for Car, Truck Awards
-- B y   C r a i g   T r u d e l l
-- 2011-12-15T18:17:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/bmw-honda-ford-vw-among-finalists-for-car-truck-awards.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG (BMW) , Honda
Motor Co.,  Ford Motor Co. (F)  and  Volkswagen AG (VOW)  were among the
automakers with models that are finalists for North American Car
and Truck of the Year awards from the Automotive Press
Association.  Ford’s Focus, VW’s Passat and  Hyundai Motor Co. (005380) ’s Elantra
are the car finalists, the association disclosed at an event in
Detroit.  BMW’s X3, Honda’s CR-V and Jaguar  Land Rover  Plc’s Range
Rover Evoque were the truck finalists. Jaguar Land Rover is part
of  Tata Motors Ltd. (TTMT)   To contact the reporter on this story:
Craig Trudell in Detroit at 
